"},{"pid":"06db99c88ac169a87cc724bf5ca4e5aea1731695","tid":519750,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中华万岁！﻿</span></span>"},{"pid":"25887eb5574459c65980206b5b8b1b02c0ce771d","tid":519750,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d89350470e67c3d67b41526a7bf693ccaa677776","tid":519750,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c5b841456ba4b67ae86035457f85ee3e40a885a","tid":519750,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f81910c4698a6d3e217832a2fbd862f381f9209c","tid":519750,"uid":48633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">汉奸！</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"唔好笑撚死人啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋班被馬克思主義的胡人夠膽叫人漢奸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"中国当代马克思主义核心只有两点，第一唯物论，第二实践检验真理。估计说了你也不懂，你也仅仅只知道&ldquo;马列&rdquo;两个字而已或者西方马克思言论。<br />\n<br />\n对于你贴的马克思的个人生平我表示呵呵<br />\n<br />\n打个比方吧，我说&ldquo;你是狗&rdquo;，难道因为我是魔鬼，我个人生活糜烂，就能证明&ldquo;你是狗&rdquo;不对吗？<br />\n<br />\n你或许还可以把马克思吃过多少饭，拉过多少屎，干过多少女人也贴出来。<br />\n<br />\n蛮夷之地出来的人思想眼界就是狭隘，估计美国佬的学校没有教你什么思想理论政治哲学体系之类的吧，多向苑举正教授学一下吧<br />\n<br />\n鬼岛新唐人的狗。最后送你四个字&ldquo;狗拿耗子&rdquo;，估计你的后代也会接你的班。好好当你的美国狗不好吗，非要在这里指点江山？中共命运怎么样关你屁事？怎么不见你去拯救伊拉克难民呢？﻿"},{"pid":"edc7e5ae556bd44f83dc8304af8a99b65f1391e5","tid":519750,"uid":134226,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"好啊<br />\nGod save our gracious Queen!<br />\nLong live our noble Queen!<br />\nGod save the Queen!<br />\nSend her victorious,<br />\nHappy and glorious,<br />\nLong to reign over us:<br />\nGod save the Queen!<br />\n事頭婆萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2809d403c420354e85de4ecada5eb9d8e4f632a0","tid":519750,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edc7e5ae556bd44f83dc8304af8a99b65f1391e5","tid":519750,"uid":134226,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"好啊<br />\nGod save our gracious Queen!<br />\nLong live our noble Queen!<br />\nGod save the Queen!<br />\nSend her victorious,<br />\nHappy and glorious,<br />\nLong to reign over us:<br />\nGod save the Queen!<br />\n事頭婆萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共应该把这些人统统送到英国。滚出中国领土﻿</span></span>"},{"pid":"10f6c7a4c06697352dc1d230f495774efdd271e8","tid":519750,"uid":108610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你要是想港独，我还敬你是条汉子。还特么回归英国，简直就是认贼作父﻿<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"24d8718749514c3b3a81e33566f83b4c80086a45","tid":519750,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"還唱甚麼義勇軍進行曲<br />\n這是由反黨、漢奸、賣國賊田漢所寫的<br />\n要唱就唱老大哥的國歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GK-LTpIVMFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGK-LTpIVMFE&d=vkLC1Gs2YKliaZsspXAvpm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ccc14312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GK-LTpIVMFE</a>"},{"pid":"516960ead864676ad78262aab72a02d7c1efb330","tid":519750,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"Btw,有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"284fc28a066b486889482eeb9544a966763a07a2","tid":519750,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"516960ead864676ad78262aab72a02d7c1efb330","tid":519750,"uid":811